These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, pink
City: rome, new-york
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, october
House: tower, wooden
1. the tower house is not to the right of the person traveling to new-york##8
2. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
3. the person who likes black is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Color      | pink     | black      |
| City          | new-york | rome    |
| Birthday         | october   | may |
| House   | tower  | wooden      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker
2 different pets are kept: frog, pony
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, aristoff
There 2 different types of food: apricot, plum
1. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the swisher-smoker##5
3. the aristoff-smoker is not to the right of the swisher-smoker##8
4. the person eating apricot is not the owner of the pony##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Game    | mah-jongg        | poker    |
| Pet       | frog         | pony |
| Cigar         | aristoff | swisher   |
| Food   | apricot               | plum  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, pall-mall
City: boston, edinburgh
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, collecting
2 different games are played: chess, monopoly
1. the person who's hobby is baking is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8
3. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Cigar   | old-henry       | pall-mall |
| City   | boston       | edinburgh    |
| Hobby   | baking | collecting |
| Game           | chess        | monopoly   |

