House: colonial, cottage
1. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the bluemaster-smoker##5
2. the person eating broccoli is not to the left of the cottage house##8
3. the cottage house is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
