There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, cola
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, dannemann
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, reggae
1. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Job   | paramedic | lawyer |
| Beverage   | cola    | tea     |
| Cigar         | bolivar  | dannemann    |
| Music-Genre     | reggae     | r&b       |

