2 different games are played: scrabble, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the person playing scrabble is not the fan of trance##6
4. the fan of trance is not to the right of the person playing scrabble##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
